573
00:32:15,860 --> 00:32:23,660
♫ Hateful bandits ♫

574
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:29,940
♫ You can’t get away from my place ♫

575
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:36,540
♫ He is sadly crying ♫

576
00:32:36,660 --> 00:32:41,460
♫ I capture the culprit ♫

577
00:32:42,100 --> 00:32:48,180
♫ Like a bird without wings ♫

578
00:32:48,700 --> 00:32:53,060
♫ He is unable to escape from my halberd ♫

579
00:32:53,860 --> 00:32:58,820
♫ He is cornered, horse’s hoof soaked in blood ♫

580
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:04,300
♫ Enemies are defeated and killed ♫

581
00:33:06,350 --> 00:33:08,160
Bear it and then run away.

582
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:22,540
♫ Tear him into pieces ♫

583
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:37,160
Ning Jiulang

584
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:39,110
is so bold.

585
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:42,640
Forgive me, Your Highness.

586
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:45,470
I thought he was capable.

587
00:33:45,470 --> 00:33:47,470
He’s just a coward.

588
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:50,310
He dared to spoil the show.

589
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:52,350
You see?

590
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,830
A talent

591
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:57,680
was frightened by a performer.

592
00:33:57,880 --> 00:34:00,230
Don’t pretend to be a hero.

593
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:03,430
Reflect on your misdeeds for three months.

594
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,350
No salary half a year.

595
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:17,840
Jiulang.

596
00:34:19,909 --> 00:34:20,710
Ning Jiulang.

597
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,469
I insulted you.

598
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,120
Why did you save me?

599
00:34:51,389 --> 00:34:58,910
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

600
00:35:01,430 --> 00:35:02,710
-Bravo!
-Good.

601
00:35:11,670 --> 00:35:22,870
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

602
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,520
I’d like to announce

603
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:28,280
Ning Jiulang comes back out of retirement.

604
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:41,080
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

605
00:36:11,390 --> 00:36:12,430
Mr. Liu.

606
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:15,520
Times change.

607
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:19,600
Why did we meet by this way?

608
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:22,430
Jiulang.

609
00:36:23,870 --> 00:36:26,230
I’m still confused by this question.

610
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:30,630
Why did you save me back then?

611
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:34,230
Performers

612
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:36,120
don’t know politics,

613
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:40,600
but operas are all about justice.

614
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:43,470
Decades have passed.

615
00:36:45,870 --> 00:36:49,760
Liu Hanyun is still Liu Hanyun.

616
00:36:50,430 --> 00:36:53,800
I didn’t misjudge you.

617
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:56,840
Thank you.

618
00:36:58,630 --> 00:37:01,800
I’ve been watching operas for decades,

619
00:37:03,430 --> 00:37:06,630
but I never have a chance to watch yours.

620
00:37:07,390 --> 00:37:08,360
Today

621
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:11,120
you watched.

622
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:13,840
Yes, I did.

623
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,910
Finally.

624
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:19,950
Rest assured, Jiulang.

625
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:22,760
As long as I’m alive,

626
00:37:23,470 --> 00:37:26,870
you can perform in Peking as you please.

627
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:48,560
Help yourself.

628
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:50,470
Here.

629
00:37:50,870 --> 00:37:52,600
Shang. Here.

630
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:54,040
Sit beside me.

631
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,520
Today

632
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,870
you fulfilled one of my wishes.

633
00:38:00,390 --> 00:38:03,120
Father. I don’t know politics.

634
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:05,760
Don’t laugh at me if I ask wrong questions.

635
00:38:06,870 --> 00:38:08,120
Just ask.

636
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:11,280
You inspect in five provinces.

637
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:13,080
You are like the imperial envoy

638
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,630
in operas, right?

639
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:19,040
You can say so.

640
00:38:19,390 --> 00:38:20,870
Would you interfere

641
00:38:20,870 --> 00:38:23,280
if someone is wronged?

642
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:26,950
Who? You?

643
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:28,120
Not me.

644
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:30,320
Zhou Xiangyun in Yunxi Theater,

645
00:38:30,950 --> 00:38:33,630
who played the maid in the Tale of Dragon.

646
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:35,230
I

647
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:37,430
invited him to perform in Shuiyun Theater,

648
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:40,760
and offended the leader of Yunxi Theater.

649
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:43,000
He had Zhou Xiangyun’s title deed

650
00:38:43,390 --> 00:38:45,000
and nearly beat him to death.

651
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,840
I know this boy.

652
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,470
He’s good.

653
00:38:49,600 --> 00:38:51,840
He doesn't deserve this.

654
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,280
I can help you with this.

655
00:38:54,670 --> 00:38:58,080
But I can’t get him back with bare hands. Right?

656
00:38:58,280 --> 00:39:00,150
As long as Yunxi can let him go,

657
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:02,800
I will pay all the money.

658
00:39:05,470 --> 00:39:06,630
Commander Cao comes.

659
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:09,560
-Commander Cao comes.
-Commander Cao comes.

660
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:10,470
Commander Cao, you’re here.

661
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:15,840
-Commander Cao.
-Commander.

662
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:16,800
Wanjun.

663
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:18,630
Feng’er.

664
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:20,950
You call me Feng’er in public again.

665
00:39:20,950 --> 00:39:22,560
That’s a girl’s name.

666
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:24,600
Some men are no better than girls.

667
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,670
You’re not a girl.

668
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:29,360
Come. This is Mr. Liu,

669
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,670
Liu Hanyun, the commissioner.

670
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:31,800
This is my brother-in-law.

671
00:39:33,600 --> 00:39:34,840
Mr. Liu.

672
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:38,120
I know you have come to Peking long ago.

673
00:39:38,120 --> 00:39:41,150
I should have received you,

674
00:39:41,150 --> 00:39:44,630
but my health is too poor. Doctor didn’t let me out.

675
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,280
I have to rest.

676
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:48,000
So, I come late.

677
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:50,120
Please forgive me.

678
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,000
Commander Cao.

679
00:39:52,910 --> 00:39:54,840
Hundreds of thousands of troops in North China

680
00:39:55,470 --> 00:39:57,760
are under your command.

681
00:39:58,760 --> 00:40:00,120
Who dares to offend you?

682
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:01,230
You’re flattering me.

683
00:40:01,520 --> 00:40:02,280
Please.

684
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:04,320
Shang.

685
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:06,230
Shang. Sit.

686
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,000
Shang.

687
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:11,670
Commander.

688
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,600
What show will you perform today?

689
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:18,120
Broken Bridge.

690
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:19,560
Broken Bridge?

691
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:23,120
That’s Kun opera.

692
00:40:23,870 --> 00:40:24,910
It’s too nagging.

693
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:26,470
That’s for girls.

694
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:29,870
Change it. Perform Qin opera.

695
00:40:29,870 --> 00:40:31,430
That’s mind-blowing.

696
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:34,600
Sit.

697
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:36,000
Wanjun. Wanjun.

698
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:37,430
Let’s drink.

699
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:38,800
Sit here.

700
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,600
Take my seat. Take my seat.

701
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,910
-OK.
-Sit.

702
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,870
I don’t think

703
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:49,910
you should order Qin opera.

704
00:40:50,470 --> 00:40:52,080
Let me order for you.

705
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:54,390
Capture and Release Cao.

706
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:57,870
Why?

707
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,390
Cao Cao

708
00:41:00,630 --> 00:41:02,040
has the same surname as you.

709
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:06,520
Here. Let’s drink.

710
00:41:08,360 --> 00:41:09,390
Reasonably speaking,

711
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:11,760
this banquet is for you.

712
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,470
I should listen to you.

713
00:41:13,870 --> 00:41:14,760
But

714
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:16,150
we should

715
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,870
watch Bao Zheng.

716
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:19,870
Bao Zheng is righteous.

717
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:23,190
You want to be as righteous as Bao Zheng.

718
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:26,630
Whether you can or not,

719
00:41:27,430 --> 00:41:29,910
let’s watch it first.

720
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:33,910
The opera doesn’t matter.

721
00:41:34,470 --> 00:41:36,950
The point is that it should be pleasing

722
00:41:36,950 --> 00:41:37,840
and

723
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,870
how he will perform.

724
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,670
You have a point.

725
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:45,670
Let me introduce a new friend.

726
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:48,390
Chang Zhixin,

727
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:51,670
the prosecutor.

728
00:41:53,190 --> 00:41:53,840
Drink a toast

729
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:55,710
to Commander Cao in my stead.

730
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,360
Handsome.

731
00:42:00,190 --> 00:42:00,840
Shang.

732
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:03,080
Return a toast for me.

733
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:07,190
I should

734
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,760
toast to you.

735
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,870
You don’t know.

736
00:42:10,870 --> 00:42:14,710
Mr. Chang is my wife’s cousin.

737
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,710
Is it true?

738
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:19,950
Commander Cao.

739
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:21,760
Mr. Chang

740
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:25,630
is in charge of Laozi Ridge’s case.

741
00:42:26,430 --> 00:42:28,470
He looks like a scholar,

742
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:31,230
but he is fearless

743
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:33,150
when he interrogates bandits.

744
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,040
Good.

745
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:35,870
Insightful and courageous.

746
00:42:37,390 --> 00:42:39,120
He should be promoted.

747
00:42:39,870 --> 00:42:41,390
Since commander has given the order,

748
00:42:41,390 --> 00:42:44,320
congratulations, cousin.

749
00:42:47,950 --> 00:42:49,120
OK. You guys drink.

750
00:42:49,430 --> 00:42:51,470
Commander Cao, Mr. Cao.

751
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,760
Would I borrow you for a moment?

752
00:42:52,910 --> 00:42:53,710
OK. OK.

753
00:42:57,230 --> 00:42:58,000
Drink.
